column5: Got a great deal on a lot of lures today, There was one that came with it and it has no brand name on it, It,s older from what I can tell by the hardware used.  So,  thoughts or anyone know what it is? It comes accross as a kwikfish.  Oh and yes, Im going to use it. Unless it,s worth millions of dollars.LOL
flatfish in a dress  lol
I've never seen one like that.

It almost looks like somebody Magyvered 2 different lures and added a blade, half kwikfish and half torpedo. I'll be the first to say kwikedo and avoid someone (like me) who'll slap the first person to say it!  Michael
Quickfish wearing a prophylactic? I don't know how it's going to track in the water with the red dress on it. It looks Frankenlured for sure. Give it a cast and report back G.

One off prototype?  I have a one off lure from a guy that tried his hand at lure design.  That's my guess anyway.
